com.inqwell.any

Interface StringI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Any, Serializable, Value
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnyString, ConstString, ConstStringDecor, NativeDescriptor.EnumString

    public interface StringI
extends Value
    The string value type interface. Concrete implementations are the mutable and const classes and the const decorator for use when constness is required to be dynamic.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.2 $
    Author:
